data.description: Enjoy this Immaculate One Level Living Twin home and private lot. With 3 beds, 3 baths, 12 ft ceilings, beautiful-scraped factory engineered floors, generous living space & stylish finishes; you'll enjoy this townhome. Natural light flows throughout the main living space.  The spacious kitchen opens to the dining area and living room. The updated gourmet kitchen features Birch cabinets, Cambria counters, Stainless appliances, quiet close drawers, pull outs, ample counter, and cabinet space. All your living on one level with main floor laundry.  Primary bedroom has walk-in closet and ensuite with Cambria counters, dual sinks, mirrors, walk-in shower and separate tub. Main level 2nd BR makes a perfect office. The expansive lower level opens to a spacious amusement room with gas fireplace, bedroom, storage room, and 3/4 bathroom. Private screened in porch off the living room is ideal for relaxing and grilling in the summer.
